name: Stark Interface
body:
### Welcome to Stark Interface!

```
$ cd StarkInterface/StarkInterface
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Concept
StarkInterface is putting the whole concept of virtual reality into a new light with a full immersive world that gives you the capability to control your real world using the virtual.

### Authors and Contributors:
2014, Mohammed Omar (@MohammadKOmer), Eduardo Preciado (@3ddo), and Nasr-Kyrillos Kelliny (@Nkelliny).
